claim: The Supernatural pilot got its premiere on The WB.
premise_source_doc_sentence: The Supernatural pilot introduced the characters of Sam  (  Jared Padalecki  )  and Dean Winchester  (  Jensen Ackles  )  , brothers who travel throughout the country hunting supernatural creatures , as they battled a ghostly Woman in White  (  Sarah Shahi  )  while searching for their missing father  (  Jeffrey Dean Morgan  )  .
